// String doubled-delimiter escape tests (BT-743)
// Doubling the delimiter ("") inside a string produces a literal double-quote.

// Single embedded double-quote
""""
// => "

// Size of a 1-char string containing `"`
"""" size
// => 1

// Embedded quotes in the middle of a string
"say ""hello"" please"
// => say "hello" please

// Multiple embedded quotes
"one "" two "" three"
// => one " two " three

// String containing two double-quotes
""""""
// => ""
